    <title>Intent</title>

    <para>
        Enable business services to receive service call-backs (or events), and be decorated with additional
        infrastructure capabilities, without having a life-cycle tied to the infrastructure, nor
        being aware of the various event sources and decorations.
    </para>
    <para>
        Business services and infrastructure services can be deployed/un-deployed independently.
    </para>

